main: this module allocates memory for the main variables of the code and calls all necessary functions with the needed parameters

input_processing: this module processes the input given by the user sets the flages and calls the other modules accordingly

match_line: this module checks if a line matches the search_phrase (while taking the flages into consideration) and returns true or false accordingly 

flages_collection: a collection of flges that are set by input_proccesing according to the input arguments

counters_collection: a collection of counters being used by the other modules

print: this module contains all the functions that print to screen
